document_title: Testicular pain: 12 causes, symptoms, and prevention
subsection_name: dau-tinh-hoan.json_4_Risk factors increase the risk of disease
subsection_content: Boys and men of all ages can experience testicular pain. Among them, the risk group is people who do heavy work or regularly play sports that require full contact. (5)
